918
00:57:04,890 --> 00:57:07,660
Nope. No one's getting fired.

919
00:57:07,660 --> 00:57:11,020
Oh, but the CEO will be replaced, though.

920
00:57:11,020 --> 00:57:13,470
The buyer wants to manage it directly.

921
00:57:13,470 --> 00:57:17,040
