What I send isn't enough.

946
00:59:09,110 --> 00:59:13,190
So she works part-time at a flower shop to help out.

947
00:59:13,190 --> 00:59:15,970
The owner even asked

948
00:59:15,970 --> 00:59:20,000
if she'd be interested in buying the business…

949
00:59:21,570 --> 00:59:26,220
but I'm short on funds.

950
00:59:26,950 --> 00:59:30,610
How much do you need?

951
00:59:33,230 --> 00:59:37,590
I have some savings,

952
00:59:38,120 --> 00:59:41,350
but I still need about a billion won.

953
00:59:42,340 --> 00:59:45,410
I know you've worked hard for us,

954
00:59:45,410 --> 00:59:47,500
but a severance package exceeding

955
00:59:47,500 --> 00:59:49,630
Sanin's regulations will be difficult.

956
00:59:49,630 --> 00:59:52,490
As you know, our company

957
00:59:52,490 --> 00:59:55,200
isn't well off financially right now.

958
00:59:57,350 --> 00:59:58,850
Yes...

959
00:59:58,850 --> 01:00:01,800
But still, if the due diligence goes well,

960
01:00:01,800 --> 01:00:05,130
there will be a chance to negotiate your severance package.

961
01:00:05,130 --> 01:00:08,490
I'll do my best when that time comes.

962
01:00:19,120 --> 01:00:21,470
Ball!

963
01:00:24,660 --> 01:00:26,410
Hey!

964
01:00:26,410 --> 01:00:27,460
Come here.

